Problem statement : Write a program to find the sum of the given series 1+2+3+ . . . . . .(N terms) 
Solution (C++) :
class Solution {
  public:
    long long seriesSum(int n) {
        long long x=0;
        x=(long long)n*(n+1)/2;//Type conversion
        return x;
    }
};
Explanation : 
Sum of first n natural numbers can be found using formula n*(n+1)/2.
Here using formula and type casting it to required data type we get the result.
